    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear and still retaining that new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no expense spared. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly pristine example that requires absolutely nothing.",
