    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a refined balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has been thoroughly vetted to ensure mechanical consistency and structural integrity, presenting a clean profile that reflects its history of responsible ownership. Ideal for those seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience without the depreciation of a new model, this vehicle stands ready for immediate service.",
      "price": 34800.0,
